001525; Stamnes, K., Tsay, S.-C., Wiscombe, W., Jayaweera, K., Numerically stable algorithm for discrete-ordinate-method radiative transfer in multiple scattering and emitting layered media (1988) Appl. Optimizat., 27, pp. 2502-2509; Velders, G.J.M., Anderson, S.O., Daniel, J.S., Fahey, D.W., McFarland, M., The importance of the Montreal Protocol in protecting climate (2007) P. Natl. Acad. Sci. USA, 104, pp. 4814-4819; (1994) Scientific Assessment of Ozone Depletion, , World Meteorological Organization (WMO) Global Ozone, Research and Monitoring Project - Report 37, Geneva, Switzerland; (1998) Scientific Assessment of Ozone Depletion, , World Meteorological Organization (WMO) Global Ozone, Research and Monitoring Project - Report 44, Geneva, Switzerland 1999; (2002) Scientific Assessment of Ozone Depletion, , World Meteorological Organization (WMO) Global Ozone, Research and Monitoring Project - Report 47, Geneva, Switzerland; (2006) Global Ozone, Research and Monitoring Project - Report 50, 2007. , World Meteorological Organization (WMO) Scientific Assessment of Ozone Depletion Geneva, Switzerland; Wuebbles, D.J., Weighing functions for ozone depletion and greenhouse gas effects on climate (1995) Annu. Rev. Energ. Env., 20, pp. 45-70; Wuebbles, D.J., Patten, K.O., Johnson, M.T., Kotamarthi, R., The new methodology for Ozone Depletion Potentials of shortlived compounds: N-propyl bromide as an example (2001) J. Geophys. Res., 106, pp. 14551-14571; Wuebbles, D.J., Patten, K.O., Three-Dimensional Modeling of HCFC-123 in the Atmosphere: Assessing Its Potential Environmental Impacts and Rationale for Continued Use (2009) Environ. Sci. Technol., 43, pp. 3208-3213; Youn, D., Choi, W., Lee, H., Wuebbles, D.J., Interhemispheric differences in changes of long-lived tracers in the middle stratosphere over the last decade (2006) Geophys. Res. Lett., 33, pp. L03807. , doi:10.1029/2005GL024274","Wuebbles, D. J.; Dept. of Atmospheric Sciences, University of Illinois at Urbana-Cham